sequenceDiagram
	autonumber
	participant UI as UI/Admin
	participant API as Go API
	participant DB as Postgres
	participant MQ as EMQX MQTT
	participant DEV as Device

	UI->>API: POST /api/devices/:idOrUuid/configuration (config JSON)
	API->>DB: INSERT device_configurations (status=pending)
	DB-->>API: config_id
	API->>MQ: PUBLISH {imei}/ondemand
	Note over API,MQ: command.name=apply_device_configuration\nmsgid=correlation_id=config_id
	MQ-->>DEV: DELIVER apply_device_configuration
	DEV->>DEV: Validate + apply config
	alt success
		DEV->>MQ: PUBLISH {imei}/ondemand (ondemand_rsp)
		Note over DEV,MQ: correlation_id=config_id\nstatus=ack|acked|success
		MQ-->>API: Deliver response
		API->>DB: Finalize device_configurations (acknowledged)
	else failure
		DEV->>MQ: PUBLISH {imei}/ondemand (ondemand_rsp)
		Note over DEV,MQ: correlation_id=config_id\nstatus=failed
		MQ-->>API: Deliver response
		API->>DB: Finalize device_configurations (failed)
	end
